T Remark OpenLab Control nested simulation example
T Set Datafile open|create experiment.dat
T Set Temperature 300.000 K at 10.000 K/min in Settle mode
T Scan Temperature 300.000 K to 299.800 K in 2 steps at 10.000 K/min, Settle
T     Scan Field 0.000000 T to 0.020000 T in 3 steps at 0.500000 T/min, Settle
T         Measure devices=transport
T     End Scan
T End Scan
T Scan Time 2.0 secs in 3 steps
T     Measure devices=transport
T End Scan
T End Sequence
